<inglise> Commission Regulation (EEC) No 2931/87 of 30 September 1987 amending Regulation (EEC) No 2213/76 on the sale of skimmed-milk powder from public storage </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 2931/87, millega muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 2213/76 l&otilde;ssipulbri m&uuml;&uuml;gi kohta riigiladudest </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> 30. september 1987 EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 804/68 of 27 June 1968 on the common organization of the market in milk and milk products (1), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 773/87 (2), and in particular Article 7 (5) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 27. juuni 1968. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 804/68 piima- ja piimatooteturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 773/87, eriti selle artikli 7 l&otilde;iget 5, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas it is specified at point (a) of Article 2 (1) of Commission Regulation (EEC) No 2213/76 (3), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 349/87 (4), that the skimmed-milk powder is to be sold at a price equal to the purchase price applied by the intervention agency at the time of conclusion of the sales contract plus 1 ECU per 100 kilograms; whereas the market situation for skimmed-milk powder is such that a reduction of 1 ECU per 100 kilograms in required in the sale price; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2213/76 (viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 349/87) artikli 2 l&otilde;ike 1 punktiga a on ette n&auml;htud, et l&otilde;ssipulbrit tuleb m&uuml;&uuml;a m&uuml;&uuml;gilepingu s&otilde;lmimisel sekkumisasutuse kohaldatava ostuhinnaga, millele lisandub 1 ek&uuml;&uuml; 100 kilogrammi kohta; l&otilde;ssipulbrituru olukord n&otilde;uab l&otilde;ssipulbri m&uuml;&uuml;gihinna alandamist 1 ek&uuml;&uuml; v&otilde;rra 100 kilogrammi kohta; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas for certain uses skimmed-milk powder must meet specific quality requirements; whereas in order to enable purchasers to check the quality of the powder it should be made possible for samples taken from the powder to be analysed before conclusion of a sales contract; </inglise>
<eesti> teatavate kasutusotstarvete puhul peab l&otilde;ssipulber vastama konkreetsetele kvaliteedin&otilde;uetele; selleks et ostjad saaksid l&otilde;ssipulbri kvaliteeti kontrollida, tuleks enne m&uuml;&uuml;gilepingu s&otilde;lmimist v&otilde;imaldada l&otilde;ssipulbri proovide anal&uuml;&uuml;simine; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the Management Committee for Milk and Milk Products has not delivered an opinion within the time limit set by its chairman, </inglise>
<eesti> piima- ja piimatooteturu korralduskomitee pole oma eesistuja m&auml;&auml;ratud t&auml;htaja jooksul arvamust esitanud, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 of Regulation (EEC) No 2213/76 is hereby amended as follows: </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevaga muudetakse m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2213/76 artiklit 2 j&auml;rgmiselt. </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> In paragraph 1 (a), 'plus 1 ECU per 100 kilograms' is deleted. </inglise>
<eesti> L&otilde;ike 1 punktist a kustutatakse tekst "millele lisandub 1 ek&uuml;&uuml; 100 kilogrammi kohta". </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The following paragraph is added: </inglise>
<eesti> Lisatakse j&auml;rgmine l&otilde;ige: </eesti>
<inglise> '3. </inglise>
<eesti> "3. </eesti>
<inglise> The intervention agency shall make whatever arrangements are necessary to enable interested parties to examine at their cost before conclusion of the sales contract samples taken from the skimmed-milk powder put up for sale. </inglise>
<eesti> Sekkumisamet teeb k&otilde;ik vajalikud korraldused, mis v&otilde;imaldavad huvitatud pooltel enne m&uuml;&uuml;gilepingu s&otilde;lmimist oma kulul kontrollida m&uuml;&uuml;giks pakutava l&otilde;ssipulbri proove." </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the day of its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub selle Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas avaldamise p&auml;eval. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 30 September 1987. </inglise>
